            <p>Rev. Dr. PEREIRA MENDES&#44;<lb/>
                New York City.<lb/></p>
            <p>Rev Dr Morais<lb/>
                My dear Sir<lb/></p>
            <p>My friend Mr Brandon asks me<lb/> for a line to you to beg you to kindly see to the case<lb/> of a young man in whom he is much interested.<lb/></p>
            <p>The young man is in one of your Institutions and Mr Brandon<lb/> thinks he may require the last duties to be soon performed<lb/> for him&#44; in which case it is earnestly desired that<lb/> everything be conducted in the orthodox method.<lb/></p>
            <p>Mr Brandon will no doubt state further particulars.<lb/>  Will you kindly see to the matter and oblige<lb/> Yrs with kindest regards<lb/> Pereira Mendes<lb/></p>
            <p>27 W 16<lb/>
                Nov 7&#47;89<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
